metadata.dc:description: The paper is a review of the jugulotympanic paragangliomata seen in our Hospital in a 2 years term. The AA. discuss every case and achieve a checking of several therapeutics procedures accepted for these growths.
metadata.dc:title: Paraganglioma yugulotimpánico: nuestra experiencia en dos años.
[Jugular-tympanic paraganglioma: our experience in 2 years].
